attributes.Long form description: The student assembles a rolling cart. He first assembles the base frame, and then assembles the first set of two bar sides. At first he misses, and then he gets them both right, assembles and screws them together. Then he gets the second set of two bar sides right, assembles and screws them together, and he slides the bottom tray and assembles it to the bars and bolts the bracket. One of the brackets is hard to do, but it does. He slides the middle tray and the top tray. He first assembles and bolts the top tray bracket, and then assembles and bolts the middle tray bracket, and he finally bolts the wheels.
